Rainbow External php-opencloud - Project License and Terms of Use

1. Introduction and Project Overview

Rainbow External Link Cloud Storage (hereinafter referred to as "the Software") is a PHP-based cloud storage and external link sharing application designed to provide users with a versatile platform for file uploading, storage, and external link generation. The software supports the upload of files in all formats, enabling users to create external links for various types of content, including general files, images, music, and video. It automatically generates both UBB and HTML codes for the generated external links, allowing seamless integration into websites, forums, and other platforms.

The software goes beyond being just a cloud storage solution; it functions as a comprehensive image hosting service and online music streaming platform. Its advanced version supports integration with major cloud storage services such as Alibaba Cloud OSS, Tencent Cloud COS, Huawei Cloud OBS, UpYun, and Qiniu Cloud. Additionally, it features image compliance detection capabilities, ensuring adherence to content regulations.

