8. Use of the Software

The Software is designed for cloud storage and external link sharing purposes. It supports the upload of files in all formats and can generate external links for various content types. The software also automatically generates UBB and HTML codes for the generated external links, enabling easy integration into various platforms. The software provides online preview functionality for text, images, music, and videos, making it a versatile platform that functions as both a cloud storage solution and an image hosting service or online music streaming platform.

9. Cloud Storage Integration

The advanced version of the software supports integration with major cloud storage services, including Alibaba Cloud OSS, Tencent Cloud COS, Huawei Cloud OBS, UpYun, and Qiniu Cloud. This integration provides users with scalable and reliable cloud storage solutions, enabling them to manage their files and external links effectively. The integration ensures seamless synchronization and management of files across different cloud storage platforms.

10. Image Compliance Detection

The software features image compliance detection capabilities, which help ensure that uploaded images comply with content regulations and guidelines. This feature automatically scans uploaded images to detect and flag potentially non-compliant content, helping maintain the integrity and legality of the platform.

11. Data Security and Privacy

The Software prioritizes data security and privacy. It incorporates various security measures to protect user data, including the use of secure protocols for data transmission and storage. The software implements user authentication and authorization mechanisms to ensure that only authorized users can access and manage their files. It also provides tools for users to manage their privacy settings and control the visibility of their files and external links.

12. Performance and Scalability

The Software is designed to be scalable and performant, supporting large volumes of file uploads and external link generation. It leverages various optimization techniques to ensure fast file uploads, quick link generation, and seamless user experience. The software also provides tools for administrators to monitor and optimize system performance.

13. Compatibility and Cross-Platform Support

The Software is compatible with various platforms and environments, ensuring broad accessibility and usability. It supports integration with different cloud storage services, providing users with flexibility in choosing their preferred storage solutions. The software is designed to be responsive and user-friendly, providing an optimal experience across different devices and browsers.

14. Updates and Maintenance

The Software is regularly updated to address security vulnerabilities, fix bugs, and introduce new features. Users are encouraged to keep their installations up to date to benefit from the latest improvements and security enhancements. The development team provides comprehensive documentation and support to assist users with updates and maintenance tasks.

